Package: expranno
Type: Package
Title: Expression Annotation, Metadata Integration, Deconvolution, and Signature Analysis
Version: 2.4.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      given = "Dai",
      family = "Dai",
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
      email = "daik54015@gmail.com"
    )
  )
Author: Dai Dai [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Dai Dai <daik54015@gmail.com>
Description: Provides a reproducible RNA-seq workflow that starts from an
    expression matrix with Ensembl gene identifiers and sample metadata,
    annotates genes for human and mouse with a coverage-first hybrid strategy,
    aligns and merges expression with metadata, reports annotation coverage,
    runs cell deconvolution through immunedeconv, and computes pathway or
    signature scores with GSVA or ssGSEA using user-supplied gene set
    databases.
